In [3]:
def drawBoxPlot(data , name) :
    data = data.dropna()
    df = pd.DataFrame(data)
    plt.title(name) 
    _, bp = df.boxplot(vert=False , return_type='both')
    print("Quantile :")
    print(df.quantile([0.25 ,0.5 ,0.75]))
In [7]:
def findOutliers(data , name) :
    Q1 = data.quantile(0.25)
    Q3 = data.quantile(0.75)
    IQR = Q3 - Q1
    right_whisker = Q3 + 1.5*IQR
    left_whisker = Q1 - 1.5*IQR
    right_region = []
    left_region = []
    right_outlier = []
    left_outlier = []
    for i in range(len(data)) :
        if(data[i] > right_whisker) :
            right_region.append(df1["region"][i])
            right_outlier.append(data[i])
        elif(data[i] < left_whisker) :
            left_region.append(df1["region"][i])
            left_outlier.append(data[i])
    r = {"region":right_region , name:right_outlier}
    l = {"region":left_region , name:left_outlier}
    df_r = pd.DataFrame(r)
    df_l = pd.DataFrame(l)
    print("Right outliers :")
    if(len(df_r.index) != 0) :
        print(df_r)
    print("The number of right outliers :" , len(df_r.index))
    print("Left outliers :")
    if(len(df_l.index) != 0) :
        print(df_l)
    print("The number of left outliers :" , len(df_l.index))

In [16]:
def forward_selection(input_df, depv="y", indepv = ["x1"]):
    selected = []
    candidates = indepv.copy()

    best_adjr2 = -1
    best_subset = []

    while len(candidates) > 0:
        # print("Current Candidates: ", candidates)
        tmp_indep_subset = []
        tmp_model_adjr = []
        tmp_model_nindep = []

        for acandidate in candidates:
            tmplist = selected.copy()
            tmplist.append(acandidate)
            modelstr = depv + " ~ " + "+".join(tmplist)
            result6tmp = smf.ols(modelstr, data=input_df).fit()
            #print(df18_result6tmp.summary())
            tmp_indep_subset.append(tmplist)
            tmp_model_adjr.append(result6tmp.rsquared_adj)
            tmp_model_nindep.append(len(tmplist))
        
        #find the best element
        tmp_adjr2 = np.array(tmp_model_adjr)
        tmpind = tmp_adjr2.argmax()
        this_adjr2 = tmp_adjr2[tmpind]
        selected = tmp_indep_subset[tmpind]

        if this_adjr2 <= 0:
            raise("Encounterd negative Adj R2. Stop.")
        # 
        # print("===============")
        # print("Current best model: ", selected)
        # print("Current best AdjR2: ", this_adjr2)


        if this_adjr2 > best_adjr2:
            #print(" best result updated")
            best_adjr2 = this_adjr2
            best_subset = selected


        candidates = set(candidates) - set(selected)
        candidates = list(candidates)

    #print out the best result
    print("best_adjr2 = ", best_adjr2)
    print("best_subset = ", best_subset)

    #run the best model again
    modelstr = depv + " ~ " + "+".join(best_subset)
    result_dropAll= smf.ols(modelstr, data=input_df).fit()
    print(result_dropAll.summary())
